{"tid":1657461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 獲提名競逐2020諾貝爾和平獎","createTime":"2019-10-16T05:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T06:49:28.000Z","uid":303778,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"87655ee78c486d2386d646da46254c97e023e0cc","tid":1657461,"uid":303778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"2019/10/16-12:27<br />\n立場報道<br />\n<br />\n今早，美國眾議院會議上全體議員一致同意 （unanimous）通過《香港人權與民主法案》，為不少努力抗爭的港人打了一支強心針。此外，挪威自由黨成員 Guri Melby 昨日（15日）亦宣布已提名全體香港人競逐 2020 年的諾貝爾和平獎，希望可以藉此鼓勵港人繼續以「非暴力方式」進行抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E6%94%BF%E5%AE%A2%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%94%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%AB%B6%E9%80%90-2020-%E8%AB%BE%E8%B2%9D%E7%88%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E7%8D%8E-%E7%9B%BC%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258C%25AA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E9%2580%2590-2020-%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25B2%259D%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%258D%258E-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%2580%25B2%25E8%25A1%258C%2F&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=d5497a42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258C%25AA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E9%2580%2590-2020-%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25B2%259D%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%258D%258E-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E7